      "writtenOn": "2018-12-11T15:55:16Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The copy of \u003cwinnt.h\u003e that I’m looking at has a “buggy” comment for ARM64 CONTEXT_* ContextFlags. It just duplicates the 32-bit ARM comment, so Fp is missing and it lists R0-R12 instead of X0-X28.\n\nThe reason I was looking was because I wanted to assure that Fp is covered by CONTEXT_CONTROL and not CONTEXT_INTEGER.",
      "revId": "5461373818b006ba49158b6c05328cf314195886",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
